MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 549588358}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 826cdd9cb8d36d946bc976f177f75c3b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::a
  introPanel: {fileID: 3068833}
  introText: {fileID: 1751429800}
  noiDungIntro:
  - The damp, musty smell of the straw mat pulled me from a restless sleep
  - Instinctively, my hand tightened around the cold hilt of the pitch-black katana
    resting by my pillow.
  - I quickly threw on my black kimono, lightly tracing the familiar yellow stripes
    on the sleeves
  - They must still be certain that I perished at the bottom of the abyss that day.
  - I quickly threw on my black kimono, lightly tracing the familiar yellow stripes
    on the sleeves
  - They must still be certain that I perished at the bottom of the abyss that day.
  - But the only thing that died was the mercy of the man who calls himself a samurai.
  - Glancing through the narrow window crack, the silhouette of the ancient castle
    still loomed faintly through the thick fog.
  - That place hides the rotten justice I must reclaim with my own hands.
  - Brushing back my long hair, I secured the blade to my waist and forcefully slid
    the door open.
  - The game of hide-and-seek is over; today, the black blade will speak.
  tocDoHienIntro: 3
  vnCanvas: {fileID: 1668995927}
  uiCanvasGroup: {fileID: 1668995929}
  textNoiDung: {fileID: 1067056201}
  textTenNhanVat: {fileID: 1387352800}
  nutBamToanManHinh: {fileID: 41556347}
  anhNhanVat1: {fileID: 0}
  anhNhanVat2: {fileID: 1804119152}
  mauSang: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  mauToi: {r: 0.5, g: 0.5, b: 0.5, a: 1}
  tocDoChu: 0.05
  amThanhGoChu: {fileID: 0}
  doMeoTieng: 0.738
  nguonPhatNhac: {fileID: 0}
  nhacNenVN: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a70c749196ad69b4c848e9c24a36269d, type: 3}
  amLuongNhac: 0.5
  danhSachTen:
  - DENKI
  - DENKI
  - DENKI
  danhSachThoai:
  - The freezing dawn wind slashed across my face, sweeping away the dry leaves crumbling
    beneath my boots
  - "The path leading to that castle is unnervingly quiet, as if death itself is
    holding its breath in anticipation\t"
  - Just keep walking; for the blood of those who stand in my way will soon warm
    this blade
  aiDangNoi: 010000000100000001000000
  playerScript: {fileID: 0}
